<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shì yīn yé sū 迦南838</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shì yīn yé sū wǒ men cái néng xiāng féng, shì yīn yé sū wǒ men cái néng tóng gōng.
 shì yīn yé sū wǒ men cái néng hé mù xiāng chù, shì yé sū ràng wǒ men tóng gān kǔ.
 lái a wǒ men jiāng róng yào guī gěi zhǔ, yīn tā xíng shì cóng bù shī wù.
 sī xiǎng tā de ēn diǎn, qí miào yòu wú shù. wǒ de líng jìn bù zhù yào xiàng zhǔ huān hū.
 wǒ de líng jìn bù zhù yào xiàng zhǔ huān hū.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>838</hymn_number>
</song>